 "data": "@startuml

' Define interfaces
interface Addable {
 +addWaste(double waste)
}
interface Calculate {
 +calculateWaste() throws InvalidWasteException
}
interface Clearable {
 +clearWaste()
}

' Define exceptions
class ComparisonException {
 -message : String
 +ComparisonException(String message)
 +toString() : String
}
class InvalidWasteException {
 -message : String
 +InvalidWasteException(String message)
 +toString() : String
}

' Define abstract classes
abstract class WaterThing {
 -waterAmount : double
 +WaterThing(double waterAmount)
 +getWaterAmount() : double
 +setWaterAmount(double waterAmount)
 +getType() : String
 +toString() : String
}
abstract class ReportGenerator {
 +generateReport()
}
abstract class WasteComparator {
 +compareWaste(double personWaste, double industrialWaste) throws ComparisonException
}

' Define classes
class IndustrialWater {
 -industrialSet : Set<Double>
 +IndustrialWater(double waterAmount)
 +addWaste(double waste)
 +addWaste(String wasteName, double wasteAmount)
 +clearWaste()
 +calculateWaste() : double
 +getType() : String
 +toString() : String
}
class PersonWater {
 -wasteList : List<Double>
 +PersonWater(double waterAmount)
 +addWaste(double waste)
 +addWaste(String wasteName, double wasteAmount)
 +clearWaste()
 +calculateWaste() : double
 +getType() : String
 +toString() : String
}
class WasteCalculator {
 +compareWaste(double personWaste, double industrialWaste) : double
 +toString() : String
}
class Yappers {
 -reportContent : StringBuilder
 +Yappers()
 +addSection(String section)
 +addEducationalSection()
 +getReportContent() : String
 +generateReport()
}
class FinalReport {
 -content : String
 +FinalReport(String content)
 +generateReport()
}
class WaterWasterApp {
 +main(String[] args)
}

' Relationships
Addable <|.. IndustrialWater
Addable <|.. PersonWater
Calculate <|.. IndustrialWater
Calculate <|.. PersonWater
Clearable <|.. IndustrialWater
Clearable <|.. PersonWater

WaterThing <|-- IndustrialWater
WaterThing <|-- PersonWater

ReportGenerator <|-- Yappers
ReportGenerator <|-- FinalReport

WasteComparator <|-- WasteCalculator

IndustrialWater ..> InvalidWasteException : throws
PersonWater ..> InvalidWasteException : throws
WasteCalculator ..> ComparisonException : throws
WaterWasterApp ..> PersonWater : uses
WaterWasterApp ..> IndustrialWater : uses
WaterWasterApp ..> WasteCalculator : uses
WaterWasterApp ..> Yappers : uses
WaterWasterApp ..> FinalReport : uses
